ps://www.investopedia.com/terms/b/ballpark-figure.asp" target=3D"_blank" re=
l=3D"noopener">Ballpark figures</a>: A single page contains 500 words with =
a single space and 250 words with double space.</p><hr><h2>Why choose our W=
ords to Pages Converter?</h2><p>The words to pages provide the correct <a h=
ref=3D"https://www.editpad.org/tool/word-counter">word count</a> of any pag=
